In England, in the seven days to 05 October, there were 193,005 new confirmed cases (341.3 new cases per 100,000). There is no change in cases compared to those confirmed in the previous week (seven days to 28 September). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 10 October is 6,936,327 (12,265.8 cases per 100,000 population).
